    <!-- ================= ABOUT ================= -->
    <section id="about" class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>About Me</h2><p>Passionate Developer | Lifelong Learner | Problem Solver</p></div>
        <div class="about-container">
<img src="assets/images/profile.png" alt="Michael Waweru">
            <div class="about-content glass">
                <h3>Who is JaydonDevHub?</h3>
                <p>I'm <strong>Michael Waweru</strong>, a software developer from Kenya who enjoys creating responsive websites, modern user interfaces, desktop applications and solving real-world problems through technology.</p>
                <p>My journey into programming started with curiosity, and today I'm continuously improving my skills in Web Development, Java, Python, SQL and modern software engineering practices.</p>
                <div class="about-details">
                    <div><strong>Name</strong><span>Michael Waweru</span></div>
                    <div><strong>Country</strong><span>Kenya 🇰🇪</span></div>
                    <div><strong>Speciality</strong><span>Software Development</span></div>
                    <div><strong>Status</strong><span>Available for Freelance</span></div>
                </div>
                <a href="assets/Michael_Waweru_Resume.pdf" class="btn" download>Download CV</a>
            </div>
        </div>
