        <div class="skills-grid">
            <div class="skill-card glass"><i class="fa-brands fa-html5"></i><h3>HTML5</h3><div class="progress"><span style="width:95%"></span></div><small>95%</small></div>
            <div class="skill-card glass"><i class="fa-brands fa-css3-alt"></i><h3>CSS3</h3><div class="progress"><span style="width:90%"></span></div><small>90%</small></div>
            <div class="skill-card glass"><i class="fa-brands fa-js"></i><h3>JavaScript</h3><div class="progress"><span style="width:88%"></span></div><small>88%</small></div>
            <div class="skill-card glass"><i class="fa-brands fa-java"></i><h3>Java</h3><div class="progress"><span style="width:82%"></span></div><small>82%</small></div>
            <div class="skill-card glass"><i class="fa-brands fa-python"></i><h3>Python</h3><div class="progress"><span style="width:80%"></span></div><small>80%</small></div>
            <div class="skill-card glass"><i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i><h3>SQL</h3><div class="progress"><span style="width:85%"></span></div><small>85%</small></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ================= SERVICES ================= -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>What I Do</h2><p>Services I can offer</p></div>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card glass"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i><h3>Web Development</h3><p>Building responsive and modern websites using current web technologies.</p></div>
            <div class="service-card glass"><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i><h3>Software Development</h3><p>Developing desktop and web applications that solve practical problems.</p></div>
            <div class="service-card glass"><i class="fa-solid fa-palette"></i><h3>UI / UX Design</h3><p>Creating clean and attractive user interfaces with excellent user experience.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ================= FEATURED PROJECT ================= -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>Current Focus</h2></div>
        <div class="featured-project glass">
            <div>
                <span class="badge">🚧 In Development</span>
                <h2>County Skills Registry System</h2>
                <p>A modern platform connecting skilled professionals with county governments. The system is currently under active development and will feature user registration, verification, intelligent search and job matching.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ================= PROJECTS ================= -->
    <section id="projects" class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>Featured Projects</h2><p>Some of my recent work</p></div>
        <div class="projects-grid">
            <div class="project-card glass">
                <img src="assets/images/weather.jpg">
                <div class="project-info"><h3>Weather Dashboard</h3><p>Real-time weather application with forecast functionality.</p><a href="#" class="btn">View Project</a></div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card glass">
                <img src="assets/images/calculator.jpg">
                <div class="project-info"><h3>Cyber Dev Calculator</h3><p>A modern cyber-themed calculator built using HTML, CSS and JavaScript.</p><a href="https://github.com/JaydonDevHub/Cyber---dev-calculator" target="_blank" class="btn">GitHub</a></div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card glass">
                <img src="assets/images/trial.jpg">
                <div class="project-info"><h3>Trial Website</h3><p>Responsive website showcasing frontend development skills.</p><a href="https://github.com/JaydonDevHub/trial_website" target="_blank" class="btn">GitHub</a></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ================= EXPERIENCE ================= -->
    <section id="experience" class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>Experience & Education</h2><p>My learning journey</p></div>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item glass"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><h3>Software Development Student</h3><small>2024 - Present</small><p>Studying software engineering, databases, networking, web technologies, and programming while developing practical projects.</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-item glass"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><h3>Frontend Development</h3><small>2024 - Present</small><p>Building responsive websites with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript using modern UI design principles.</p></div>
            <div class="timeline-item glass"><div class="timeline-dot"></div><h3>Backend Development</h3><small>2025 - Present</small><p>Learning Java, Python, and SQL while creating complete and scalable software solutions.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ================= GITHUB ================= -->
    <section id="github" class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>GitHub Activity</h2><p>Building and learning continuously</p></div>
        <div class="github-grid">
            <div class="glass github-card"><h3>Repositories</h3><h1 id="repo-count">--</h1></div>
            <div class="glass github-card"><h3>Followers</h3><h1 id="followers-count">--</h1></div>
            <div class="glass github-card"><h3>Following</h3><h1 id="following-count">--</h1></div>
            <div class="glass github-card"><h3>Public Projects</h3><h1 id="project-count">--</h1></div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>Latest GitHub Repositories</h2><p>Recent projects from my GitHub profile.</p></div>
        <div id="github-repositories" class="projects-grid"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- ================= CONTACT ================= -->
    <section id="contact" class="section">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>Let's Work Together</h2><p>Have a project in mind? Let's talk.</p></div>
        <div class="contact-container">
            <div class="contact-info glass">
                <h3>Contact Information</h3>
                <p>I'm always open to discussing software projects, collaborations, freelance opportunities, and innovative ideas. Feel free to reach out!</p>
                <div class="contact-item"><i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i><span>+254 111 498 830</span></div>
                <div class="contact-item"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i><span>github.com/JaydonDevHub</span></div>
                <div class="contact-item"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i><span>RealMe</span></div>
                <div class="contact-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i><span>Nairobi, Kenya</span></div>
            </div>
            <form class="glass">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>
                <input type="email" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Subject">
                <textarea rows="7" placeholder="Write your message..." required></textarea>
                <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ================= FOOTER ================= -->
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <h2><span>JD</span> JaydonDevHub</h2>
            <p>Creating software that solves real-world problems.</p>
            <div class="footer-social">
                <a href="https://github.com/JaydonDevHub" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/254111498830" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i></a>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/RealMeMike" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <p>© 2026 Michael Waweru | JaydonDevHub. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        </div>
